# CI/CD Pipeline

## Workflows

| Workflow | Trigger | What it does |
|----------|---------|--------------|
| `ci.yml` | PR, push to main | fmt, clippy, nextest, doctests, cargo-deny, MSRV check |
| `lint-pr.yml` | PR title change | Validates conventional commit format |
| `dependabot-issues.yml` | Dependabot PR | Creates tracking issues for dependency updates |
{%- if has_releases %}
| `release.yml` | Push to main | Detects releasable commits via git-cliff, creates version tags |
{%- endif %}
{%- if has_binary_dist %}
| `cd.yml` | Tag `v*.*.*` | Cross-platform binary builds, GitHub Release, optional publishing |
{%- endif %}
{%- if has_releases and not has_binary_dist %}
| `publish.yml` | Tag `v*.*.*` | GitHub Release, optional crates.io publish |
{%- endif %}
{%- if has_site %}
| `deploy-site.yml` | Push to main | Build and deploy documentation site |
{%- endif %}
{%- if has_benchmarks %}
| `benchmarks.yml` | Manual, schedule | Run divan + hyperfine benchmarks |
{%- endif %}
{%- if has_roadmap_votes %}
| `roadmap.yml` | Issue vote threshold | Roadmap voting automation |
{%- endif %}

## Composite Actions

Reusable action fragments in `.github/actions/`, shared across workflows.

| Action | Used by | Purpose |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `setup-cargo-tools` | ci, {% if has_binary_dist %}cd, {% endif %}{% if has_benchmarks %}benchmarks{% endif %} | Install and cache cargo tools via binstall |
| `setup-rust-cache` | ci{% if has_binary_dist %}, cd{% endif %} | Cargo build cache with target-specific keys |
| `bot-setup` | {% if has_releases %}release{% endif %} | Configure git bot identity for automated commits |
{%- if has_releases %}
| `generate-release-changelog` | {% if has_binary_dist %}cd{% else %}publish{% endif %} | Extract version from tag + generate changelog via git-cliff |
{%- endif %}
{%- if has_site %}
| `setup-site-deps` | deploy-site | Install site dependencies ({{ npm }}) |
{%- endif %}

{%- if has_releases %}

## Release Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    PUSH["push to main"] --> CI["ci.yml"]
    PUSH --> REL["release.yml"]
    REL --> CHECK{"releasable<br/>commits?"}
    CHECK -->|no| DONE["done"]
    CHECK -->|yes| TAG["create tag v*.*.*"]
{%- if has_binary_dist %}
    TAG --> CD["cd.yml"]
    CD --> GRC["generate-release-changelog"]
    CD --> BIN["binary builds<br/>8 targets"]
    BIN --> GHR["GitHub Release<br/>(via artifact upload)"]
    GRC -.->|changelog| GHR
    BIN --> CRATES["crates.io"]
    BIN --> BREW["Homebrew"]
    BIN --> NPM["npm"]
    BIN --> DEB[".deb"]
    BIN --> RPM[".rpm"]
    style CRATES stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style BREW stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style NPM stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style DEB stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style RPM stroke-dasharray: 5 5
{%- else %}
    TAG --> PUB["publish.yml"]
    PUB --> GRC["generate-release-changelog"]
    GRC --> GHR["GitHub Release"]
    GRC --> CRATES["crates.io"]
    style CRATES stroke-dasharray: 5 5
{%- endif %}
```

_Dashed boxes are opt-in via repo variables (e.g. `CRATES_IO_ENABLED`)._
{%- endif %}
